videos.headline: Ballage strikes first for ASU
videos.description: Kalen Ballage takes it in from one-yard out for the Sun Devils' touchdown.

videos.headline: Browning evades defenders and throws for first down
videos.description: Washington quarterback Jake Browning buys himself time evading multiple defenders and finds Lavon Coleman across the field who scrambles for a first down.

videos.headline: ASU has trouble in backfield
videos.description: Kalen Ballage and Kyle Williams collide on a jet sweep, resulting in a loss of two yards for Arizona State.

videos.headline: Petersen: 'They're just playing better than us'
videos.description: Washington head coach Chris Petersen thinks his defense is doing a good job against Arizona State in the first half despite being down 13-0.

videos.headline: Browning converts on 4th down
videos.description: Jake Browning throws a tight pass to Hunter Bryant on 4th-and-3 to keep Washington's drive alive in the 3rd quarter.

videos.headline: Washington kept off the board with missed FG
videos.description: Van Soderberg misses a 27-yard field goal for Washington in the 3rd quarter.

videos.headline: Washington misses another FG
videos.description: Van Soderberg misses a 21-yard field goal by hitting the upright as Washington remains off the board.

videos.headline: Browning dives to get Washington a TD
videos.description: Jake Browning finally gets Washington on the board with a quarterback sneak late in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Wilkins hurdles a defender
videos.description: Arizona State quarterback Manny Wilkins hurdles another defender on a six-yard run.

videos.headline: Arizona State's bold fourth-down seals game
videos.description: Manny Wilkins gets lucky as he overthrows a receiver, but finds Ceejhay French-Love for a 30-yard gain into the Washington red zone.

videos.headline: Jordan Miller leaves game on cart
videos.description: Washington defender Jordan Miller has to leave the game on a cart after a leg injury.

videos.headline: Graham: 'Great night to be a Sun Devil'
videos.description: Todd Graham couldn't be prouder of the way his team performed and expected them to step up.

videos.headline: How does Washington's loss impact CFB landscape?
videos.description: Dave Pasch and Greg McElroy discuss a weekend of upsets and the rest of the College Football season.
